794
01:03:18,879 --> 01:03:20,297
Right fucking above us.

795
01:03:22,174 --> 01:03:23,008
Get her!

796
01:03:23,092 --> 01:03:26,178
You fucking moron! I thought
you were our ace sniper.

797
01:03:27,388 --> 01:03:30,349
