909
01:27:51,183 --> 01:27:52,518
Please, help me!

910
01:27:52,601 --> 01:27:54,186
Please, stop.

911
01:27:57,398 --> 01:27:58,399
Oh, thank God.

912
01:28:10,661 --> 01:28:14,331
Thank you so much
for stopping. I...

913
