retired from the CIA.

944
01:31:17,097 --> 01:31:18,098
Officially.

945
01:31:22,311 --> 01:31:24,688
The Global Response
and Intelligence Team.

946
01:31:26,690 --> 01:31:27,900
I do it my way,

947
01:31:28,651 --> 01:31:29,693
with my people.

948
01:31:32,446 --> 01:31:33,446
